## 4. Key Features & Components

### A. Authentication
*   **Sign Up/Login**: Users authenticate using Email/Password.
*   **JWT Storage**: Tokens are stored in `localStorage` and managed via `AuthContext`.
*   **Role Setup**: Users have roles (`USER` or `ADMIN`). The UI adapts based on this role (e.g., Admin Dashboard link appears only for Admins).

### B. Project Management
*   **Create Campaign**: A form [CreateCampaign.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CreateCampaign.jsx) sends data to `POST /projects`. It validates required fields like "Funding Goal" and "Description".
*   **View Campaigns**: [Home.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/Home.jsx) fetches all projects (`GET /projects`).
*   **Project Details**: [CampaignDetails.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CampaignDetails.jsx) is the heart of the user experience.
    *   Displays progress bars for funding.
    *   Shows "Days Left" and "Backers".
    *   **Tabs**: Governance (Revenue/Expenses), Story, Transparency.

### C. Financial & Governance Engine
This is the unique "Fintech" aspect of the platform.

1.  **Funding**: Users contribute funds via `POST /finance/contribute` in [CampaignDetails](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CampaignDetails.jsx#11-379).
2.  **Expense Requests**:
    *   Creators upload bills via [CreatorDashboard](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CreatorDashboard.jsx#7-225) (`POST /expenses`).
    *   These appear as "Pending" in [CampaignDetails](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CampaignDetails.jsx#11-379).
3.  **Governance Voting**:
    *   **Admins** (representing the Governance Council) can Approve/Reject expenses directly in [CampaignDetails](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CampaignDetails.jsx#11-379).
    *   *Design Note*: Real-time calling of `PATCH /expenses/:id/status` releases funds instantly.
4.  **Revenue Sharing**:
    *   Creators ingest external revenue (e.g., from Ads) in [CreatorDashboard](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/CreatorDashboard.jsx#7-225).
    *   They can trigger "Global Distribution" to pay back all token holders proportionally.

### D. Admin Dashboard ([AdminDashboard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Omkar%20Raut/OneDrive/Desktop/TSEC_Hacks_26/frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx))
A protected route `/admin` accessible only to `ADMIN` users.
*   **Risk Reports**: Fetches AI-generated risk flags from the backend.
*   **Wallet Freezing**: Allows admins to freeze a project's funds if suspicious activity is detected.

